    "id": "v37"
  }, "v37"), mdx("p", null, "M\xF9a m\xE0ng t\u1ED1t \u0111\u1EB9p c\u1EE7a x\u1EE9 thu\u1ED9c v\u1EC1 c\xE1c vua m\xE0 Ng\xE0i \u0111\u1EB7t l\xEAn th\u1ED1ng tr\u1ECB ch\xFAng t\xF4i, v\xEC t\u1ED9i l\u1ED7i ch\xFAng t\xF4i. C\xE1c vua \u0111\xF3 h\u1ED1ng h\xE1ch th\u1ED1ng tr\u1ECB ch\xFAng t\xF4i v\xE0 gia s\xFAc ch\xFAng t\xF4i, cho n\xEAn ch\xFAng t\xF4i g\u1EB7p kh\u1ED1n \u0111\u1ED1n.Giao \u01B0\u1EDBc c\u1EE7a d\xE2n ch\xFAng "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v38"
  }, "v38"), mdx("p", null, "V\xEC nh\u1EEFng l\xFD do \u0111\xF3, nay ch\xFAng t\xF4i l\u1EADp m\u1ED9t giao \u01B0\u1EDBc vi\u1EBFt ra ch\u1EEF. C\xE1c v\u1ECB l\xE3nh \u0111\u1EA1o, c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u1EDDi L\xEA-vi, v\xE0 c\xE1c th\u1EA7y t\u1EBF l\u1EC5 \u0111\xF3ng \u1EA5n h\u1ECD v\xE0o \u0111\xF3.\""), mdx("hr", null), mdx("p", null, "", mdx("a", {
